OL,3,CHow Mandelson flunked the vetting but
OL,4,Cstill became US ambassador
OL,6,FAnother was grilled on his religious
OL,7,Fbeliefs and said he was asked whether
OL,8,Fhe could be trusted to defend the UK,
OL,9,Fgiven he spends a good deal of time in
OL,10,FFrance.
OL,12,FBoth were approved to do their
OL,13,Fsensitive jobs.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
