OL,3,CHow Mandelson flunked the vetting but
OL,4,Cstill became US ambassador
OL,6,FThey also said that in every case they
OL,7,Fknew of where UK Security Vetting had
OL,8,Fadvised that an individual should not
OL,9,Fbe passed as fit and proper - where
OL,10,Fthe recommendation was not to grant
OL,11,F"Developed Vetting" status in the
OL,12,Fjargon - the relevant individual was
OL,13,F"marched out of the building, never to
OL,14,Freturn".
OL,16,FNot so Peter Mandelson.
OL,26,@sD@AOUsD@SO]uD@AOUvD@GO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/11
