OL,3,CHow Mandelson flunked the vetting but
OL,4,Cstill became US ambassador
OL,6,FThe government's vetting experts at UK
OL,7,FSecurity Vetting recommended he should
OL,8,Fnot be granted security clearance for
OL,9,Fthe hugely important and sensitive
OL,10,Fpost of British ambassador in
OL,11,FWashington. But they were overruled by
OL,12,Fthe foreign office's most senior
OL,13,Fofficial, Olly Robbins, the permanent
OL,14,Funder-secretary, and Mandelson took up
OL,15,Fthe swanky post.
OL,17,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,18,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,19,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,20,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
