OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776453069
OL,3,CHow Mandelson flunked the vetting but
OL,4,Cstill became US ambassador
OL,6,FNow I am told the Foreign Office is
OL,7,Funusual, probably unique, in being
OL,8,Fable to ignore the advice of UK
OL,9,FSecurity Vetting. The Home Office has
OL,10,Fno such discretion. But the Foreign
OL,11,FOffice exploits this power only rarely.
OL,13,FWhy did Robbins do so?
OL,15,FGiven that Mandelson resigned in
OL,16,Fdisgrace last September, following
OL,17,Frevelations of his too-close
OL,18,Frelationship with the late convicted
OL,19,Fpaedophile billionaire, Jeffrey
OL,20,FEpstein, it was plainly a bad decision.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
