OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776453069
OL,3,CHow Mandelson flunked the vetting but
OL,4,Cstill became US ambassador
OL,6,FAnother question is why Robbins didn't
OL,7,Ftell either the foreign secretary or
OL,8,Fthe prime minister that Mandelson had
OL,9,Fbeen classified as a security risk.
OL,11,FThe prime minister learned this only
OL,12,Fdays ago, says Downing Street. And the
OL,13,Fdeputy prime minister, who was foreign
OL,14,Fsecretary at the time, David Lammy,
OL,15,Fwas informed only today!
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
