CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776453069
OL,3,CHow Mandelson flunked the vetting but
OL,4,Cstill became US ambassador
OL,6,FA third question is why Robbins didn't
OL,7,Ftell Keir Starmer that Mandelson had
OL,8,Fflunked the vetting test shortly after
OL,9,FStarmer held a press conference in
OL,10,FHastings in February this year -
OL,11,Fbecause at that press conference
OL,12,FStarmer told a lie, albeit
OL,13,Funintentionally, that Mandelson had
OL,14,Fpassed the vetting process.
OL,16,FStarmer compromised himself, and would
OL,17,Fhave wanted to set the record straight
OL,18,Fforthwith. Mendacity, albeit
OL,19,Faccidental, is a terrible look for the
OL,20,Fhead of the government.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
