PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776453069
OL,3,CHow Mandelson flunked the vetting but
OL,4,Cstill became US ambassador
OL,6,FThe leader of the opposition, Kemi
OL,7,FBadenoch, thinks he is so compromised
OL,8,Fthat he needs to resign.
OL,10,FThere is no sign tonight that Starmer
OL,11,Fis set to take her advice. But if
OL,12,FRobbins has embarrassed the prime
OL,13,Fminister by not telling him in a
OL,14,Ftimely way that Mandelson flunked the
OL,15,Fvetting, it is difficult to see how he
OL,16,Fcould keep his job.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
