PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776453069
OL,3,CHow Mandelson flunked the vetting but
OL,4,Cstill became US ambassador
OL,6,FObviously, it would be a wholly
OL,7,Fdifferent story if Robbins could prove
OL,8,Fthat he did inform Lammy or Starmer.
OL,9,FHe has been summoned to give evidence
OL,10,Fto MPs on the Foreign Affairs Select
OL,11,FCommittee next week, so he can reveal
OL,12,Fall.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
