CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F319A1776453069
OL,3,CHow Mandelson flunked the vetting but
OL,4,Cstill became US ambassador
OL,6,FWhatever happens, Starmer is damaged.
OL,7,FBecause he knew from an earlier
OL,8,Fscrutiny assessment, run by the
OL,9,FCabinet Office, that there were
OL,10,Fconcerns about Mandelson's proximity
OL,11,Fto Epstein and about his potential
OL,12,Fconflicts of interest stemming from
OL,13,Fcorporate relationships of the
OL,14,Fconsultancy he created, Global Counsel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
