OL,3,CHow Mandelson flunked the vetting but
OL,4,Cstill became US ambassador
OL,6,FStarmer repeatedly says he made a
OL,7,Fmistake in appointing Mandelson and
OL,8,Fthat it was his fault. It won't
OL,9,Freinforce confidence in him that he
OL,10,Fdidn't apparently ask whether any
OL,11,Fconcerns about Mandelson had been
OL,12,Fbrought up by UK Security Vetting.
OL,14,FHave you heard our podcast Talking
OL,15,FPolitics? Tom and Robert dig into the
OL,16,Fbiggest issues dominating the
OL,17,Fpolitical agenda in every episode...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/11
